{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2031099e64","title":"陈伯达对教育部全体工作人员的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7ce6d7131b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":5,"articleId":"2031099e64","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"教育和教育革命","id":"299424f798","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c5b6aae222","type":"title","text":"陈伯达对教育部全体工作人员的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2031099e64","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b71959693","type":"paragraph","text":"〖摘录〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2031099e64","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa76142695","type":"paragraph","text":"我建议可以考虑组织五十来个人的班子。开会以后，组织五十个人的样子，组织一个管理教育行政的班子……我们啊，这个国家因为建国以来，学了苏联，有个缺点，国家的机构庞大。听懂吗？国家机构太庞大了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2031099e64","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ede94209b","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2031099e64","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"347e6e871b","type":"paragraph","text":"总而言之，时间是很迫切的，现在很需要一个教育行政的班子。大学要开学，中学要开学，小学要开学，还有毕业生要处理。要我处理，我处理不了。要有一个行政班子。国家迫切需要一个行政班子，国家要管理教育的行政班子，不要等得太久。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2031099e64","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}